{"tid":2327224,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨與BioNTech達成協議  首批供應大陸疫苗在德國生產","createTime":"2020-12-16T02:31:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T02:35:45.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"76461cad3922cb7a4c76979cc1e591fbd5f95cbb","tid":2327224,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T02:31:22.000Z","msg":"BioNTech和復星醫藥達成協議 首批供應內地疫苗在德國生產<br />\n<br />\n德國生物技術公司BioNTech和上海復星醫藥達成協議，只要BioNTech研發的新冠疫苗在內地獲得上市批准，<span class=\"gold\">BioNTech明年會向內地供應至少1億劑疫苗</span>，首批疫苗會由德國工廠生產。<br />\n<br />\nBioNTech感謝中國政府和國家藥監局對疫苗研發工作的支持與信任。復星醫藥形容BioNTech疫苗是國際研發合作的成功範例。<br />\n<br />\n雙方早在本年3月已經達成戰略合作協議，會共同於中國大陸和港澳台地區，開發和商品化BioNTech的mRNA技術平台研發的新冠疫苗產品，並在11月於江蘇啟動疫苗二期臨床試驗，以支持疫苗未來在中國的上市申請。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2370862\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2370862&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU%2F8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=d6e7dff2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2370862</a>"},{"pid":"c07fbac4a7f84dd5226b473481f6c6a37309dd60","tid":2327224,"uid":11540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T02:33:32.000Z","msg":"讓領導先用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d7c19d8d8e9e8f0be8a9daf01f9b332fb6919c","tid":2327224,"uid":253729,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T02:33:36.000Z","msg":"做乜唔食中藥"},{"pid":"e2674885a23e47c32be859df1e9bf128a16ead25","tid":2327224,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T02:34:35.000Z","msg":"邊度生產都無用，支那冷藏運輸同無一樣"},{"pid":"b16e2d73d7a8abe6287f82cf60e65b9029e259c9","tid":2327224,"uid":10014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T02:35:45.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>唔怪得要等到敗登勝選先公布疫苗研發成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌 對美帝徹底失望</strong></span>"}]}